nodes.name: Create job
nodes.notes:
Original curl command:
curl --location 'https://workflow.sanctifai.com/webhook-test/hgi/create-job' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--data '{
  "jobTitle": "Illustration Project",
  "jobDescription": "A project to create illustrations for a fantasy book.",
  "totalBudget": 300,
  "numberOfHires": 3,
  "taskBreakdown": "Create character designs, design cover art, and produce interior illustrations.",
  "timeline": {
    "start": "2025-03-05T00:00:00Z",
    "end": "2025-04-05T23:59:59Z"
  }
}
'

body.jobDescription: A project to create illustrations for a fantasy book.
body.taskBreakdown: Create character designs, design cover art, and produce interior illustrations.
